transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thanks for calling Viagra. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yes, let me start by giving you my email.

Speaker 1: I can take your first and last name please.

Speaker 2: Donald Aguilar, 914-73.

Speaker 1: And what's going on Mr. Aguilar? How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Okay, when was my last time I got a refill?

Speaker 1: It looks like the last time an order actually went out was way back when.

Speaker 2: You had like almost placed an order last year, but it never was approved.

Speaker 1: It wasn't approved by the doctor. I don't know why.

Speaker 2: So it's been like years.

Speaker 1: Okay, so what do I need to do for a new prescription?

Speaker 2: You just got to pay for it. I'll get set up with the doctor today.

Speaker 1: He'll pay for it. You'll pay for it, but boom.

Speaker 2: Okay, so is it the same? Before I used to get that 100 mg Viagra.

Speaker 1: Is that the same as the AGV that just came out?

Speaker 2: No, that's a different pill that you were taking before.

Speaker 1: If it's been since 2021, it's different.

Speaker 2: What's the difference with the new AGV?

Speaker 1: It lasts longer and it works faster.

Speaker 2: Does it say AGV on the pill now?

Speaker 1: Not on the pill, no. It says 100 on one side and blank on the other.

Speaker 2: I see.

Speaker 1: A buddy of mine, he said he ordered the AGV, and he did get the AGV,

Speaker 2: but he said it didn't say AGV, that he did just the regular Viagra.

Speaker 1: So if I pay for the motor, it's going to be for the AGV.

Speaker 2: Yeah, it doesn't say AGV on it, but that doesn't mean it's not.

Speaker 1: It's about the manufacturer is the thing.

Speaker 2: So it matters the company that makes it.

Speaker 1: The markings on the pill just designate it basically.

Speaker 2: So yeah, don't worry about that.

Speaker 1: That's just like marketing on the website where it says AGV.

Speaker 2: Oh, so they don't say AGV on it?

Speaker 1: No, they just have the marking.

Speaker 2: They have the milligram dosage.

Speaker 1: So if it's a 50 milligram, it'll say AGV on it.
